Migration:
############################################################


Three steps:
1) DUMP: run sophomorix-dump on old server
    (dumps to /root/sophomorix-dump)
2) copy the dir /root/sophomorix-dump recursively to new server/stick
3) SUCK IT IN: sophomorix-vampire --datadir /path/to/dumped/dir

